				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2156983&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610182413" alt="psul" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2156983)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/psul" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2156983); return false;" >psul</a></span> <span class="odate time_1457338888 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">07 Mar 2016 08:21</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2468733">
									

<p>Mobile Task Force Eta-11 (&quot;Savage Beasts&quot;) takes their bow for the 2016 MTF Contest. In this set of recovery logs and action reports, the MTF is on the hunt for the person who stole SCP-012 from containment, and goes into action against some musical anartists. Hopefully they can go out on a high note!</p>
<p>Many many thanks to the excellent Site-19 String Quartet, who have been a great team to work with. And a special thanks to the incomparable <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1621343&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1457346202" alt="SunnyClockwork" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1621343)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;">SunnyClockwork</a></span> for Eta-11's logo, used here for the first time.</p>
<p>If you're new to MTF Eta-11, there are lots of cross-links in this article, but below is the recommended reading order for the contest entries:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/a-convincing-lyre">A Convincing Lyre</a></strong></li>
<li><strong><a href="/an-impenitent-thief">An Impenitent Thief</a></strong></li>
<li><strong><a href="/project-proposal-2014-2112">Project Proposal 2014-2112: &quot;Dreams of Failure&quot;</a></strong></li>
<li><strong><a href="/scp-2402">SCP-2402</a></strong></li>
<li><strong><a href="/enjoy-the-silence">Enjoy the Silence</a></strong></li>
<li><strong><a href="/the-musical-suspects">The Musical Suspects</a></strong></li>
</ul>

							</div>

								
