<p>Thanks very much for the kind words, Hercules. Much appreciated.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>I wasn't expecting the Eta-11 contest arc to end in such a humorous way</p>
</blockquote>
<p>I agree that the the team has been quite high on the angst-o-meter. It felt like they needed a bit of catharsis.</p>
<p>On that note, it's quite deliberate that the last part of the report is the first time in the whole arc where Mike Carter has been included in the (on-page) action. In my mind, his youth and enthusiasm is an important element in bringing the team together, and adds an element of hope for the future.</p>

